                "description": "<p>Identifies the <code>MLModel</code> category. The following are the available types: </p> <ul> <li>REGRESSION -- Produces a numeric result. For example, \"What price should a house be listed at?\"</li> <li>BINARY -- Produces one of two possible results. For example, \"Is this an e-commerce website?\"</li> <li>MULTICLASS -- Produces one of several possible results. For example, \"Is this a HIGH, LOW or MEDIUM risk trade?\"</li> </ul>"
